Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you know about your brother,\Nbut you know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue speaking\Nsuch nonsense, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making this easy, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's natural though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly being told such a story\Nby a stranger like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I tell you is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi did mention it, did he not?\NAbout his accomplice that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}that{\i0} Madara Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything about Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose Itachi died\Nwithout realizing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NSuch things don't matter anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you will listen.\NYou need to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your obligation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the ninja world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of\Nthe Hidden Leaf Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And for your sake, your brother risked everything.\NYou will know how Itachi Uchiha lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Itachi implanted Amaterasu\Ninto your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi was determined to make sure\Nthat you and I would not meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You will understand why,\Nas well as everything else, when you hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who knew the truth about Itachi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,were Danzo of the Hidden Leaf, the Third Hokage,\N and his advisors Homura and Koharu. Just those four.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Hokage died...\Nand now, there are only three aging folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, those three will probably\Nnever reveal the abominable truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth about Itachi will fade\Ninto darkness forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is what Itachi wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I know the truth\Nabout Itachi too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said earlier...\NItachi died without realizing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he wanted to\Nmake doubly sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Itachi did not trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So just in case I did know the truth,\N he planned to silence me with the Amaterasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably anticipated I would show\Nmy Sharingan in order to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this guy saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Think back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Think carefully and\Nremember about Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,About your kind brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is it, right?\N{\i1}The place where Father works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the headquarters of\N{\i1}the Hidden Leaf Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've always been curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is the Uchiha crest\N{\i1}on the police force logo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? You noticed that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who wouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well...let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Simply put, it seems our ancestors formed\N{\i1}and organized this police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, they used our family crest\N{\i1}as the symbol of this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From ages past, {\i1}our clan has been\N entrusted {\i1}with the safety of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Uchiha crest reflects\N{\i1}the pride of our clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While its numbers have dwindled,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even today, nearly everyone in\N{\i1}the clan serves on Squad One
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and is dedicated to preserving\N{\i1}the peace and safety of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, only exceptional ninja are capable\N{\i1}of preventing crimes that ninja commit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father is great, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you going to work here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to take my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who would do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Foolish little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mangekyo Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you do hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what big brothers are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Sasuke... Another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:30.90,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(825.938,582.5)}Fate    \N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I took the liberty\Nof tying you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you weren't gonna stay still\Nand listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He... Itachi was my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:09:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed our parents...\NHe killed everyone in the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a Rogue Ninja...\NA member of the Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true... that he annihilated\Nthe Uchiha clan that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And he deserted the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is what he was ordered\Nto do by the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the beginning of\Nthe truth about Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, Itachi killed his personal feelings\N and fulfilled his mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've calmed down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to talk about Itachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I must take you back to the early days\Nwhen Hidden Leaf Village was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi sacrificed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fate that has continued\Nsince ages past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He was sacrificed for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge problem rooted since the time\NHidden Leaf Village was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what determined Itachi's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long story,\Nbut everything I tell you is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,On what basis should I believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're untrustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can show you\Nas proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's up to you whether\Nyou believe me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But you will hear me out until I finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine... So talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started more\Nthan 80 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The world was in turmoil.\NIt was the age of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nations battled for power and\Nto increase their territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,During this age of war, ninjas consisted\N of individual clans serving as armed units.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They were hired by various nations\Nto participate in the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And among the many ninja clans,\Ntwo were feared as the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,One was us, the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other was known\Nas the Forest's Senju Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We of the Uchiha clan possessed\Nexceptional chakra and the Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excelling in all types of warfare,\Nwe became known as a battle clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was born into the Uchiha clan,\N possessing chakra that was especially powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the fact that I've lived\Nthis long is proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in those days,\Nall I did was battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In an age defined by power,\N I sought to become ever stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and killed my friends and\Neven my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, I came into possession of the perfect\N Mangekyo Sharingan, and became the leader of the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And using that power,\NI fought the Senju clan countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was inevitable that I face Hashirama,\Nthe leader of the Senju clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wood Style" Hashirama Senju,\Nthe future first Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who stood at the top of the ninja world...\N And the one I respected most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Senju clan, led by Hashirama\Nwho became the First Hokage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,was feared and respected\Nby all the other clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Senju moved,\Nso did the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Our clan was probably the only clan\Nable to compete with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If a nation hired the Senju,\N the opposing nation would hire the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We were like rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I went up against Hashirama,\N the more my name became known as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To get close to the top...\N{\i1}to measure my abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To heighten your reputation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You took your younger brother's eyes\Njust for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I did take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I needed power in order\Nto protect the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. As the Uchiha name spread,\Nits enemies increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a necessary sacrifice to protect the clan during\N the fierce fighting with the Senju, and the other clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not for my fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My younger brother was in total agreement\N and offered his eyes to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day,\Nthe Senju clan offered a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Uchiha accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, in both clans, had grown weary of\N the fighting that had dragged on for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the only one who opposed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where has all the hate gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For what purpose had my brother\Nsacrificed himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha and Senju are\Nlike oil and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help fearing that in time,\N the Uchiha clan would come to be oppressed by the Senju clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However...everyone in the Uchiha clan\Nwanted a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As their leader, I had no choice\Nbut to go along with their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortly thereafter, the ninja alliance\Nsigned a pact with the Land of Fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,which had sought dominion\Nover the territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The secure one nation, one village system\Nwas formed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and became the Land of Fire and\Nthe Village Hidden in the Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Other countries adopted\Nthe one nation, one village system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And subsequently,\Nthe fires of war were extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Momentary peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But due to a certain incident,\N the Hidden Leaf Village quickly descended into turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight...for the First Hokage's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, the first to occupy\Nthat seat was Hashirama Senju.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Land of Fire and\Nthe entire clan chose Hashirama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was inevitable that the Uchiha's hold on\Nthe reins of power would loosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that the Uchiha\Nshould take leadership...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That we should confront Hashirama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one, not even from\Nthe Uchiha clan, supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My subordinates, who did not wish to light the\N fires of war, were unsympathetic and betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was accused of acting\Nout of greed and self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They scorned me as a selfish brother who stole his\N younger brother's eyes in order to save his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What brother would willfully\Nhurt his younger brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...I just wanted to\Nprotect the Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I became an avenger and declared\Nwar on the Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At that place which became known\Nas the Final Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was said...to have died there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Hashirama believed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone forgot about me...\NHistory forgot about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashirama's younger brother who became the Second Hokage\N was determined that there would never be a traitor like me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as proof of his trust, he granted\Nthe Uchiha a special position...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And he created\Nthe Hidden Leaf Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This was to further distance the Uchiha\Nfrom the reins of government.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it was a way to keep\Na close eye on the entire clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There were Uchiha members\Nwho realized this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Members who wanted to carry\Non my rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But...it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Senju clan solidified its hold on power\N and the Uchiha fell to becoming Senju dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I predicted came to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain other incident sealed\NUchiha's figurative demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The attack of the Nine-Tailed Fox Demon\N16 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nine-Tails can only be tamed and\N controlled by the ocular powers of the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups of Hidden Leaf Village\Nperceived the Uchiha to be behind this attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a natural occurrence,\Na natural calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet suspicion fell on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That the Uchiha had revolted\Nand sought to take power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the Uchiha was put under the\N strict surveillance of the Anbu Black Ops,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they were forced to relocate\Nto the outskirts of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They became totally estranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Hokage was the only one\Nto voice opposition to our treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Danzo of the Anbu Black Ops and the\N rest of the councilors would not listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end,\Nthe Uchiha clan was not trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the discrimination began...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Their distrust bred hatred and eventually,\Ntheir suspicions became reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha clan plotted\Na coup d'état to take over the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups in Hidden Leaf Village\Nplanted a spy within the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That spy was your older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,From that moment,\NItachi's suffering began.
